name: TreeViewItemGroup
description:
A container for nested tree items.
Renders a `<div>` element with role="group".

hiddenUntilFound.description:
Allows the browser's built-in page search to find and expand collapsed items.

Overrides the `keepMounted` prop and uses `hidden="until-found"`
to hide the element without removing it from the DOM.

className.description:
CSS class applied to the element, or a function that
returns a class based on the component’s state.

keepMounted.description: Whether to keep the element in the DOM while the item is collapsed.
